---
title: Thai-Style Sweet Chili Chicken Breasts with Cilantro-Lime Rice
description: Dinner tonight features chicken coated in a tangy sweet chili sauce coupled with zucchini and carrots. Don't forget our cilantro-lime rice, which infuses every bite with brightness!
